PurchasingSubContractorMonitoringReport is a BusinessTask
    owned by po

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for InventoryManager, PurchasingManager, Receiver, Buyer, SupplyManagementProcessor, ApplicationAdministrator, SupplyManagementViewer, Purchasing
                category is "Analysis"
                report name is "SubContractorMonitoring"
				Description
                    Monitor certification letters or audit reports for subcontractor vendors for Grant Accounting.
                    Use to evaluate all of the subcontractor purchase orders.
                    Excludes vendors that have no transactions since last certified or only recent transactions that have not been audited.
            Reports
                PurchasingSubContractorMonitoringReportReport

    Parameters
        Company                 is a PurchasingCompany 
        CertifCode              is a PO240CertifCodeArray
        PoCreateFrDate          is Date
        PoCreateToDate          is Date
        CertifEffDate           is Date
        CertifExpDate           is Date
        Vendor                  is a PO240VendorArray
        Status                  is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                OpenPurchaseOrders   value is "O"
                ClosedPurchaseOrders value is "C"
                Both                 value is "B"

    Parameter Rules
		Company
			required
		Status
			initial value is "B"
			default to "B"

    Actions
        PurchasingSubContractorMonitoringReport is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
